  <data key="d7">idence of this is infused into the mind by the Holy Ghost Who expels any fear of the contrary. It is in this sense that fortitude is reckoned a gift of the Holy Ghost . For it has been stated above ( I-II:68:1-2 ) that the gifts regard the motion of the mind by the Holy Ghost .</data>
